	in the regex for `\\(this\\)?pagestyle'

2015-08-10  Tassilo Horn  <tsdh@gnu.org>

	* latex.el (TeX-latex-mode): Call LaTeX-preview-setup only if its
	bound.

	* preview.el.in (LaTeX-preview-setup): Setup menu and keymap only
	once.

