	* doc/Makefile.in (TEXINFOINCLUDES): macros.texi has moved here
	from ../preview/doc
	(../INSTALL, ../INSTALL.windows, ../README, ../CHANGES, ../TODO)
	(../FAQ): Change dependencies accordingly.

