	* configure.ac: Recurse into preview _before_ starting any
	AC_SHELL_QUOTIFY business to avoid double quoting.

	* doc/tex-ref.tex (\title{RefTeX (long)})
	(\title{RefTeX (short)}): New columns.  One will have to go.

