	* Makefile.in (tar-ball): Remove warning which often confuses
	users.

	* aclocal.m4 (EMACS_MAJOR_VERSION): New test and variable.

	* configure.in: Fix AUCTeX version.

	* tex-site.el.in: At least (X)Emacs 21 is required.

